description: Marty McFly is a typical American teenager from California. His flabby father George is constantly ridiculed and bullied by Biff Tannen's boss, the boy's mother suffers from depression and obesity, and his older siblings are classic losers. One night in 1985, the guy meets his eccentric scientist friend, nicknamed Doc, who introduces the main character to a real time machine. But further events are not at all according to the plan of the inventor - instead of him, Marty is sent to 1955, who does not at all understand that any action can radically change the future.
cast: Michael J. Fox, Christopher Lloyd, Lea Thompson
